Titolo: Opus: Echo of Starsong

Anno: 2021

Descrizione: Opus: Echo of Starsong (stylized as OPUS: Echo of Starsong) is a text-driven side-scrolling adventure game developed by Taiwanese independent studio SIGONO. It is the third installment of the OPUS series, after Opus: The Day We Found Earth and Opus: Rocket of Whispers. Like its predecessors, the game focuses on story, puzzles and exploration.The game was released on September 1, 2021 for Microsoft Windows and macOS.

Genere: Adventure 

Valutazione: N/A
